00:34:41,128 --> 00:34:42,912
Help! Help!

737
00:34:46,745 --> 00:34:49,883
Her hands--
she's wearing mittens.

738
00:34:50,177 --> 00:34:52,091
Put the gun down, lady.

739
00:34:52,347 --> 00:34:54,690
The pie-making murderer
couldn't finish the job,

740
00:34:54,727 --> 00:34:57,021
