the muscle to finish me off?

741
00:34:57,057 --> 00:34:59,053
Ned didn't kill anyone,
and you know it.

742
00:34:59,185 --> 00:35:01,073
We're just trying to
find out the truth.

743
00:35:01,105 --> 00:35:03,751
