745
00:35:13,618 --> 00:35:15,791
And I don't think you
want to be one, either.

746
00:35:15,827 --> 00:35:18,022
Let us take the evidence
to the authorities.

747
00:35:18,115 --> 00:35:20,413
We'll find out who really
killed your brother.

748
00:35:26,587 --> 00:35:28,123
All right. You can go.

749
00:35:30,298 --> 00:35:32,942
If you can put whoever killed
my brother behind bars,

750
00:35:33,136 --> 00:35:34,422
I will be happy.

751
00:35:34,848 --> 00:35:36,222
I thought I wanted revenge,

752
00:35:36,516 --> 00:35:39,593
but all I really need
is j-j-j-justice.

753
00:35:41,557 --> 00:35:44,813
- Did she just stutter?
- Yep.

754
00:35:46,605 --> 00:35:49,101
And take your trunk
monkey with you.

