00:36:11,385 --> 00:36:14,171
<i>hours earlier than the
time the pie maker</i>

764
00:36:14,255 --> 00:36:16,591
<i>was found hovering
over the body.</i>

765
00:36:16,926 --> 00:36:19,493
<i>Fingerprint analysis of
the sheet of candy fruit</i>

766
00:36:19,527 --> 00:36:22,850
<i>exposed the nine-fingered
culprit to be none other than...</i>

767
00:36:23,145 --> 00:36:26,521
<i>Andrew Brown,
health inspector,</i>

768
00:36:26,818 --> 00:36:29,573
<i>whom, it was revealed upon
further investigation,</i>

769
00:36:29,605 --> 00:36:32,983
<i>had been blackmailing
Dilly and Billy Balsam.</i>

770
00:36:33,237 --> 00:36:36,693
<i>Having paid off the inspector to
conduct a surprise inspection</i>

771
00:36:36,988 --> 00:36:39,532
<i>that led to the pie hole's
temporary shutdown,</i>

772
00:36:39,565 --> 00:36:42,453
<i>brown had demanded a bribe,
lest he reveal</i>

773
00:36:42,507 --> 00:36:46,083
<i>Billy and Dilly's dastardly
deed and shut them down, too.</i>

774
00:36:46,157 --> 00:36:50,330
<i>Unwilling to be bullied,
Billy Balsam balked.</i>

775
00:36:57,756 --> 00:37:00,650
<i>Health inspector Andrew
Brown is now believed to be</i>

776
00:37:00,708 --> 00:37:03,701
<i>the number-one suspect in the
murder of Balsam's Bittersweets</i>

777
00:37:03,735 --> 00:37:06,563
<i>Taffy & Sweets emporium
