780
00:37:13,165 --> 00:37:14,660
<i>and released from jail.</i>

781
00:37:14,738 --> 00:37:17,042
<i>Authorities are conducting an
extensive search for Andrew Brown,</i>

782
00:37:17,078 --> 00:37:18,782
<i>who remains at large.</i>

783
00:37:18,878 --> 00:37:21,821
<i>Up next, can apes drive?
We'll find out.</i>

784
00:37:24,208 --> 00:37:25,573
Dead girl walking.

785
00:37:26,075 --> 00:37:27,781
Walking right toward me.

786
00:37:28,208 --> 00:37:29,540
Are you okay?

787
00:37:29,957 --> 00:37:31,660
Sure. I mean, I am now.

788
00:37:31,875 --> 00:37:33,330
Ned.

789
00:37:34,795 --> 00:37:37,870
- That hug goes double for me.
- Oh, double. Double hug.

790
00:37:39,928 --> 00:37:41,630
- Olive.
- What?

791
00:37:47,557 --> 00:37:48,681
Come on.

792
00:37:53,358 --> 00:37:55,732
Doing this work without you...

793
00:37:57,867 --> 00:37:59,613
Well, it actually
ends up meaning

