00:37:59,685 --> 00:38:01,440
I'm doing a whole lot of work.

795
00:38:01,948 --> 00:38:04,491
Not that I can't do it,
'cause I can.

796
00:38:05,828 --> 00:38:08,623
- I just don't like it.
- Glad to be back.

797
00:38:09,545 --> 00:38:11,623
It's not all that bad in jail.

798
00:38:11,915 --> 00:38:14,963
I had a lot of time to think,
and I came to a decision.

799
00:38:15,338 --> 00:38:17,683
Everyone talks about how
the truth will set you free,

800
00:38:17,718 --> 00:38:20,022
but burly Bruce was free to
love someone 'cause he was

801
00:38:20,057 --> 00:38:22,643
so good at lying to himself
about that doll being real.

802
00:38:22,678 --> 00:38:24,261
Which is to say...

803
00:38:24,555 --> 00:38:26,011
"Go, lying."

804
00:38:26,047 --> 00:38:29,471
Or at least "Yay to
not telling the truth."

805
00:38:33,935 --> 00:38:36,101
I'm not gonna tell
Chuck about her dad.

806
00:38:37,815 --> 00:38:40,813
I just heard that as though
it came out of my own mouth.

807
00:38:40,866 --> 00:38:43,690
- Oh, wait. It did.
- Well, you were right.

808
00:38:44,077 --> 00:38:46,282
- Good night.
- Good night.

809
00:38:51,707 --> 00:38:53,331
Welcome home.

810
00:38:53,505 --> 00:38:57,043
<i>Safely home and cleared of
