812
00:39:01,228 --> 00:39:03,050
<i>and went up to bed.</i>

813
00:39:19,238 --> 00:39:21,322
- Olive.
- Fredo.

814
00:39:22,027 --> 00:39:23,653
I knew it was you.

815
00:39:47,555 --> 00:39:49,763
<i>Sometimes, a
crime of passion</i>

816
00:39:49,806 --> 00:39:52,470
<i>is not realizing the
passion in time,</i>

817
00:39:52,737 --> 00:39:56,602
<i>while other times, the crime is
