00:40:21,468 --> 00:40:23,751
It's weird,
but I kind of like it.

821
00:40:24,007 --> 00:40:25,341
I know. Me too.

822
00:40:28,057 --> 00:40:31,181
When I was in jail,
I think you were my phantom limb.

823
00:40:33,435 --> 00:40:35,391
- I was?
- You were.

824
00:40:35,728 --> 00:40:37,972
It felt like you were
with me the whole time.

825
00:40:40,605 --> 00:40:42,401
I'm so glad you're back.

826
00:40:43,738 --> 00:40:45,863
<i>The pie maker
had never felt</i>

827
00:40:45,908 --> 00:40:48,951
<i>closer to another person
